Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:21.21,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(114,257)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}BRIDGE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:26.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is where I lost my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:35.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:39.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What was my relationship with Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:46.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:47.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:51.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can I come over to your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:54.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm... not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:55.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:59.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm... not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:15.76,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(274,295)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Body and Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:19.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:22.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't stop my heart from dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:28.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Crying and laughing, we never forget our memories together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:39.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Finding your true self
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And becoming an adult is difficult work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:45.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe I can forget for now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The night is waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:53.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As our hearts beat excitedly in rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:55.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And we frolic about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I nearly realize
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:03.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The feelings I want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:06.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even if we are afraid of the past and future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:10.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You cannot move if you remain empty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:16.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's all right if we have fun, so let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I forget all my troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:23.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and dance the night away with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:30.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll become someone more wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:34.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This endless Golden Time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The distance between us as you approach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Neither closes nor widens
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:44.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll treasure this even it it's the long way around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:57.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Until I was 18, I was Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:00.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The day after my graduation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:06.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I fell off a bridge and left my physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:10.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was ejected and became a lifeless spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:22.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the soulless and empty Banri has been living in body only, as an amnesiac,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and somehow became a college student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, as a ghost,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:32.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been watching over the newly reborn Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:34.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri can't hear me.
