Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.45,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(334,75)}{\i1}Let's go get our stuff{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.45,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(184,112)}{\i1}from the club.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.45,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(164,183)}{\i1}I want to talk to you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.45,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(150,219)}{\i1}afterward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.58,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(328,98)}{\i1}I want to talk to you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.58,Dialogue9,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(186,131)}{\i1}afterward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:46.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We've just met...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:55.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But being with you is so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:56.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:59.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I hope we can be good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:07.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:11.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now we'll match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:13.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a survivor's mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I had mine when we escaped from that cult the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I left my stuff behind, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:27.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I had this in my pocket, so I took it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:29.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:34.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've thought of it as a symbol of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:38.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanted to give you the same one, so I bought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Please accept the gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.22,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(240,146)}{\i1}To commemorate the{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.22,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(218,190)}{\i1}anniversary of our escape!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.22,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(259,230)}{\i1}From your friend,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.22,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(289,272)}{\i1}Kaga Kouko{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:00.39,Dialogue10,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(80,98)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}STUPID LINDA{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:00.39,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(335,378)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Baka Banri
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:05.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What was up yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:09.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You sounded weird over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:17.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought I might have been a little hard on Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you're worried about Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:20.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:24.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And about Chinami, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:34.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My! My!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why, if it isn't my dear friend, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now that I've run into you this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sure this will be a splendid day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:52.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We must have been destined to be great friends since a previous life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,G-good morning, Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, your voice is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:04.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, have you ever thought about our previous lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:08.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:12.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was a postulant at a convent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:16.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were a shepherd living deep in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:20.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Every morning, you delivered cheese to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that so romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:30.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:35.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful to fate for allowing me to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:37.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My, Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah... Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:46.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo, you must have been a solitary hunter wandering through the wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can tell by looking at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:59.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Given my quiet days of prayer in the convent, perhaps we were never destined to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:10.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's get started, Kouko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:20.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai was helping me register for classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This girl doesn't know a thing about mandatory courses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was telling her about some she could still take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada Banri, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:34.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Have you already registered?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:35.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Er, yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is my friend Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is Linda-senpai from the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She rescued us from the cult's overnight trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:54.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I heard my friend caused you some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was no trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, is your registration going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah... I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:01.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who's your civil law teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Uh... Tsukamoto-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:04.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're taking Tsukamoto's civil law course?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tsukamoto makes really tough exams every year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Previous exams are no help,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and he's really strict about attendance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:19.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo, you seem to have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How... sad... for... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:34.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask some other civil law professors if it's not too late to register!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Fail all your classes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stay an extra year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:42.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:46.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mitsuo is such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh... right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Have you guys decided whether you're joining the festival club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:56.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We still don't have any new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll both join.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:04.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're great friends, connected by a powerful bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We do everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:07.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Right, Tada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:09.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:13.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Great! That's two new members!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I hope we can be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,R-right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:20.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You must know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:27.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is there some reason you won't mention it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:33.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, didn't you say you weren't confident in your dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:34.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:38.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I figured that's no reason to shy away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.27,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(450,187)}Pedestrians
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.27,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(498,224)}and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.27,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(471,263)}Bicycles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.27,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(493,301)}Only
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A lot has happened recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:46.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After overcoming all of it, I'm feeling really positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:56.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to try new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be indecisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a waste of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Make progress every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:06.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to run myself to death with a super-positive lifestyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why are you being so proactive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:12.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You should be more positive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No... you have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:19.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you're not as positive as I am, you won't be the perfect friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:20.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just because I rejected-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Would someone normally say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nothing. I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But you were about to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wasn't, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:34.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I really wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:38.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then take control of this awkward pantomime act.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A-anyway, that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's give the festival club everything we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm first year law student Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:11:00.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm first year law student Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:09.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This'll help build momentum for our summer event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's happening this summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're participating in an Awa dance event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's start practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Music.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Start by imitating the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm confident that I'll dance well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:57.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were actually pretty good for beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:00.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada Banri and Kouko-chan, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be my friend!\NIt's not fair that you can dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:17.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanted to be positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why does this have to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:29.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's nothing to cry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:36.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:41.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know I'm just... lashing out at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:42.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You'll still be my friend, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:51.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know you're just being nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You joined a club with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,danced with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You listen to me complain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:06.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm just taking advantage of your kindness and causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You must hate me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:12.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't you stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's been pushing herself really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:21.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's only been two days since Yana-san rejected her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is that drink crazy enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:31.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A latte with espresso, vanilla syrup, whipped cream, caramel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's the greatest combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You seem to be feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:43.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was ridiculous of me to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,These days, I've just been...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:48.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:54.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Actually, I may have always been easily confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm stupid, hot-headed, and irredeemable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:06.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought I had to put my mistakes behind me as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And so... I panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:14.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When you say "mistakes", you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:19.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanted to deal with my feelings for Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not as though I still love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:23.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's like my emotions are still paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, no! My nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun... you're using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:39.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're matching mirrors of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:47.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada-kun, you understand my worthless self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You forgive me despite my worthlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And I took advantage of that and cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm a year older than you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're the same age as Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:07.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to be like Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I admire her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:15.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's so open, and she seems to be positively enjoying life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:18.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's cool no matter what she's doing, and she's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:23.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think Kosshi-senpai likes Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They seem close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:31.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They don't seem to be going out, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:36.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe Linda-senpai has a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After all, she is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I bet she's really popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hayashida Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your temperature is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is there something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well... it's not about my health.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:02.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Every day in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:06.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see a flickering light on that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:09.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A light?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,At night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:13.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you saying you're having trouble sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You should have said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:22.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I'm not tired yet at 11:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:25.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's lights out at 9:00 in this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You need to sleep according to the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know they're worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,After all, I have amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:43.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been hospitalized for almost two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I've been confined for observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:51.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When can I leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:54.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:17:00.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Could it be some kind of signal for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think it was this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,G-give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I mean no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:28.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... I'm a patient in the hospital down the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you're wondering what I'm doing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:37.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,it's because I can see that light from my room, and I wondered what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I came out here to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:45.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A-are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sh-should...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:55.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Should I get someone from the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, as for the rest of my story...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:03.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,someone was trying to signal to me with that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:12.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought they were signaling for me to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:15.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like it was saying, "Come with me, come with me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like I was being led here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like I should run this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm under observation all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:30.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's suffocating and boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So today, I couldn't take it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and now I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes! I am clearly stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:40.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What have you been doing alone every night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've been coming to see the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My friend's been hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:56.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't see him, though, for... reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I thought I could at least drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:01.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is he from around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I go to college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm home for Golden Week now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:12.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tokyo sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I got into a college in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I could say goodbye to this prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel like I could escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:24.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Prison? You mean the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:28.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That... and the human relationships restricting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All my ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:32.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All of that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:35.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:38.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:40.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I should go to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll leave the hospital, study,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,and get into a college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:53.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for your signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:58.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know your signal wasn't meant for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:02.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but to me, your light was a sign for me to break free!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:09.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:18.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:22.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why hasn't she said anything, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:24.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,About going to high school together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:27.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,or meeting me while I was hospitalized...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even though you have a body,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,you have no memories from before you were 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:47.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even though I have memories, I have no body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:49.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...what Linda...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:55.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...meant to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:19.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In one hand in the sweetened cafe latte I love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:23.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The moment I smiled I could smell love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:27.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to wear my cherry-colored dress perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:32.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My heart beats quietly as I rush to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:35.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,(Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:37.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watch out for that sweet trap
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:39.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,(Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:41.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll whisper to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:44.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}(Hey, I'm a little anxious)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:46.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, I long for this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.83,0:22:50.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How should I smile when I see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:53.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Pretty love, pretty love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:55.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:57.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Under the sky, under sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:00.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's hold hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:05.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't be honest about my feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:10.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But pull me along by my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:40.85,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(53,410)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yes No
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:29.97,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(106,364)}Whirr, clunk. Whirr, clunk. Whirrrr, whirrrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:31.37,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(216,365)}Kaga-san, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:31.91,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(276,365)}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:33.97,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(224,364)}Wh-whirr, whirr, whirr...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.38,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(323,362)}Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.38,0:23:36.64,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(266,365)}Kaga-san broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.65,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(109,365)}Yana-san, what am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:39.48,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(297,365)}Ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:40.85,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(261,362)}That's what I did.
